  "content": "<span>Samten Hills stands as a captivating cultural and spiritual destination for tourists</span><span>The architectural design of Samten Hills Dalat draws inspiration from the rich cultural heritage of the Himalayan region</span><span>Experience the awe-inspiring sight of the world's largest prayer wheel, crafted from bronze and adorned with 24k gold</span><p>Samten Hills in Dalat, named after the Tibetan word \"བསམ་གཏན་,\" meaning stability and balance of mind, is a cultural and spiritual tourist attraction situated on picturesque high hills in Don Duong, approximately 15km from Lien Khuong Airport. The design of Samten Hills draws inspiration from the Mandala circle, symbolizing a miniature cosmology with an extraordinary sense of the uninterrupted connection between the inner and outer worlds—creating a wonderful space with no beginning and no end. Samten Hills Dalat serves as a haven of majestic energy, harmonizing with remarkable works crafted by Lamas. The architectural style of Samten Hills is influenced by the cultural aesthetics of the Himalayas, the roof of the world, where sacred lands heal the souls that tread upon them. Notably, Samten Hills is home to the world's largest prayer wheel, the Drigung Kagyu Rinchen Khorchen Khorwe Go Gek, adding to its spiritual significance.</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sq0wdwybcvuv2bwsjjqx.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sq0wdwybcvuv2bwsjjqx.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sq0wdwybcvuv2bwsjjqx.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sq0wdwybcvuv2bwsjjqx.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>Butter lamp is a traditional practice that promotes enlightenment and spiritual growth. Butter lamps, alsoknown as dritso, are small butter-filled lamps that are lit and offered as a gesture of devotion, purification, andillumination</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/wqcyssm9xr43dhpke075.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/wqcyssm9xr43dhpke075.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/wqcyssm9xr43dhpke075.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/wqcyssm9xr43dhpke075.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>A guided meditation session, where visitors can find inner calm and rejuvenation through mindfulness practices led by experienced instructors</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/x9tgmiwzkvluig9y92nb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/x9tgmiwzkvluig9y92nb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/x9tgmiwzkvluig9y92nb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/x9tgmiwzkvluig9y92nb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>The offering of smoke is also a spiritual practice, where aromatic incense or herbs are burned as an offering.The rising smoke is believed to carry prayers and intentions for peace, healing, and blessings up to the heavens</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/kqe4811doszlijdip69n.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/kqe4811doszlijdip69n.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/kqe4811doszlijdip69n.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/kqe4811doszlijdip69n.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>The world’s largest prayer wheel is made of bronze, and covered with 24k gold, can be observed from far distance</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/gvbvgp248fwuvxd4mgco.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/gvbvgp248fwuvxd4mgco.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/gvbvgp248fwuvxd4mgco.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/gvbvgp248fwuvxd4mgco.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>Samten Hills, covering an area of 200 hectares</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/zvohb6iggxhz00epqjbs.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/zvohb6iggxhz00epqjbs.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/zvohb6iggxhz00epqjbs.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/zvohb6iggxhz00epqjbs.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>This is His Holiness's last legacy in the world, where spreading the Buddha's teachings help to bring happinessto people.</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sv0z1rqd6zmwfzuh50eb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sv0z1rqd6zmwfzuh50eb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sv0z1rqd6zmwfzuh50eb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sv0z1rqd6zmwfzuh50eb.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>Amitayus, a Buddha of Longevity, symbolizes the energy that brings health and long-life to all sentient beings.Amitayus Buddha is the enjoyment body (sambhogakaya) of Amitabha Buddha.</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sz3gkkyf7jjajqomglug.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sz3gkkyf7jjajqomglug.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sz3gkkyf7jjajqomglug.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/sz3gkkyf7jjajqomglug.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>Khata involves the presentation of a ceremonial silk scarf. Khatas are offered as a gesture of respect, goodwill,and auspiciousness</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/ujarvwspr2d6urowjer9.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/ujarvwspr2d6urowjer9.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/ujarvwspr2d6urowjer9.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/ujarvwspr2d6urowjer9.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>Samten Hills is home to the world's largest prayer wheel, the Drigung Kagyu Rinchen Khorchen Khorwe Go Gek</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/v2pnjhmzkmwy0nb0m26o.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/v2pnjhmzkmwy0nb0m26o.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 1x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/v2pnjhmzkmwy0nb0m26o.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-2,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 2x, https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/v2pnjhmzkmwy0nb0m26o.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=dpr-3,c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740 3x\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"max-width: 100%; object-fit: fill; object-position: 50% 50%;\"><p>The \"Day to Return\" package features a pizza-making workshop, where visitors can bond with family and loved ones while creating their own pizzas.</p><img importance=\"low\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset/poDPVCkaNUwmnwhQ5qWhtwj296dob8sZeluptDyLyZg=/image/upload/activities/g3xmzxwjjhay2vejreol.jpg?_src=imagekit&amp;tr=c-at_max,h-500,q-60,w-740\" srcset=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/xpe-asset